claim.claim-text:
A method for manufacturing a granular activated carbon, comprising the following steps (A) to (D) of:
(A) carbonizing an activated carbon raw material, followed by pulverization;
(B) mixing the activated carbon obtained in step (A) with a calcium component, followed by molding;
(C) carbonizing and activating the activated carbon obtained in step (B); and
(D) washing the activated carbon obtained in step (C).
